No!

01:43.536 --> 01:45.971
No, please!

01:46.038 --> 01:47.872
Can't somebody
help me?

01:47.940 --> 01:49.741
Help me!

01:50.743 --> 01:52.344
No!

02:00.619 --> 02:03.355
Help!

02:17.353 --> 02:20.105
Hey, Jack, are you ready?
We gotta go.

02:21.407 --> 02:23.325
Hey, where's the costume?

02:23.409 --> 02:24.659
It's itchy.

02:24.744 --> 02:27.379
Did you try the long sleeves
on underneath?

02:27.446 --> 02:29.381
I don't want to be
Spider-man anymore.

02:29.448 --> 02:30.882
Why not?

02:30.950 --> 02:32.317
I don't know.

02:32.385 --> 02:34.886
Ok. Well, you have to make up
your mind by tomorrow, ok?

02:34.954 --> 02:36.688
Ok.
Ok.

02:36.756 --> 02:38.556
You did a good job
on the cookies.

02:38.624 --> 02:39.874
Teamwork, right?

