there's no suspicions,

22:07.747 --> 22:09.447
there's no sign of rehab,
but he totally cleaned up.

22:09.515 --> 22:10.949
Maybe that's when
he met someone.

22:11.017 --> 22:14.219
Has he ever been arrested
with a man named Tommy Proctor?

22:14.286 --> 22:17.122
Yeah, once, uh, 2002...

22:17.173 --> 22:19.224
